SIMPLE: term_day
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Term day
<hw>Term day</hw>. <def>A day which is a term (as for payment of rent),
or is a day in a term, as of the sitting of a court; esp., one of a
series of special days, designated by scientists of different nations or
stations, for making synoptic magnetic, meteorological, or other
physical observations.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Termer</ent>⟦br⟧
